<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <%- include('./partials/head.ejs', {
    pageTitle: 'About BookLantern',
    pageDescription: 'Learn how BookLantern brings together results from globally trusted libraries so you can discover millions of books in one place.'
  }) %>
</head>
<body class="about-page" data-page="about">
  <%- include('./partials/navbar.ejs') %>

  <!-- About Header -->
  <div class="about-header">
    <div class="about-container">
      <%- include('./partials/backLink.ejs', { text: 'Back', fallback: '/' }) %>
      <h1 class="about-title">About BookLantern</h1>
      <p class="about-description">
        We bring together millions of free books from globally trusted libraries, 
        making knowledge accessible to everyone through one simple, beautiful interface.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- About Content -->
  <main class="about-main">
    <div class="about-container">
      <!-- Mission Section -->
      <section class="about-section">
        <h2>Our Mission</h2>
        <p>BookLantern exists to democratize access to knowledge. We believe that great books and educational content should be freely available to everyone, regardless of their location or economic circumstances.</p>
      </section>

      <!-- What Makes Us Different -->
      <section class="about-section">
        <h2>What makes BookLantern different</h2>
        <div class="feature-grid">
          <div class="feature-item">
            <h3>Unified Search</h3>
            <p>Search across millions of books from multiple sources in one place, without jumping between different library websites.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="feature-item">
            <h3>Clean Reading Experience</h3>
            <p>Our distraction-free reader is optimized for focus and comprehension, making long-form reading a pleasure.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="feature-item">
            <h3>Trusted Sources</h3>
            <p>All content comes from respected public domain and open access collections from globally trusted institutions.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="feature-item">
            <h3>No Barriers</h3>
            <p>Free to use, no subscriptions, no ads interrupting your reading. Just pure access to knowledge.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <!-- Promise Section -->
      <section class="about-section">
        <h2>Our Promise to readers</h2>
        <p>We're committed to keeping BookLantern free, fast, and focused on what matters most: connecting you with the books you want to read. We respect your privacy, never sell your data, and continuously work to improve your reading experience.</p>
      </section>
    </div>
  </main>

  <%- include('./partials/footer.ejs') %>
</body>
</html>

<style>
/* About Page Styles */
.about-header {
  background: var(--surface);
  border-bottom: 1px solid var(--line);
  padding: 32px 0;
}

.about-container {
  max-width: var(--container);
  margin: 0 auto;
  padding: 0 24px;
}

.about-title {
  font-size: var(--h1);
  font-weight: 600;
  color: var(--ink);
  margin: 16px 0 16px;
}

.about-description {
  color: var(--ink-weak);
  font-size: 18px;
  line-height: 1.6;
  max-width: 600px;
  margin: 0;
}

.about-main {
  padding: 48px 0;
}

.about-section {
  margin-bottom: 48px;
}

.about-section h2 {
  font-size: var(--h2);
  font-weight: 600;
  color: var(--ink);
  margin-bottom: 24px;
}

.about-section p {
  color: var(--ink-weak);
  line-height: 1.6;
  font-size: 16px;
  max-width: 700px;
}

.feature-grid {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(280px, 1fr));
  gap: 32px;
  margin-top: 32px;
}

.feature-item {
  background: var(--surface);
  padding: 24px;
  border-radius: var(--card-radius);
  box-shadow: var(--shadow);
}

.feature-item h3 {
  font-size: 18px;
  font-weight: 600;
  color: var(--ink);
  margin: 0 0 12px;
}

.feature-item p {
  color: var(--ink-weak);
  line-height: 1.5;
  margin: 0;
  font-size: 14px;
}

/* Mobile Responsive */
@media (max-width: 768px) {
  .about-header {
    padding: 24px 0;
  }
  
  .about-main {
    padding: 32px 0;
  }
  
  .about-section {
    margin-bottom: 32px;
  }
  
  .feature-grid {
    gap: 24px;
  }
  
  .feature-item {
    padding: 20px;
  }
}
</style>

  <style>
    /* Timeline Candles */
    .timeline-candles {
      position: fixed;
      top: 20%;
      right: 5%;
      z-index: 1;
      pointer-events: none;
    }

    .candle {
      width: 20px;
      height: 40px;
      background: var(--gradient-primary);
      border-radius: 10px 10px 2px 2px;
      margin: 10px 0;
      position: relative;
      animation: candle-flicker 3s ease-in-out infinite;
    }

    .candle:nth-child(1) { animation-delay: 0s; }
    .candle:nth-child(2) { animation-delay: 1s; }
    .candle:nth-child(3) { animation-delay: 2s; }

    @keyframes candle-flicker {
      0%, 100% { opacity: 0.8; transform: scale(1); }
      50% { opacity: 1; transform: scale(1.05); }
    }

    .about-hero{
      background: var(--gradient-bg);
      padding: 64px 0 24px;
    }
    .about-hero .inner{max-width:880px;margin:0 auto;text-align:center;padding:24px;}
    .about-hero h1{font-size:clamp(36px,6vw,56px);letter-spacing:-.02em;margin:0 0 12px;}
    .about-hero p{max-width:820px;margin:0 auto 16px;color:#556070;font-size:clamp(16px,2vw,20px);}
    .cta-row{display:flex;gap:10px;justify-content:center;flex-wrap:wrap;margin-top:12px;}
    .section-copy{max-width:820px;color:#556070;line-height:1.6;}
    .mt-2{margin-top:12px;}
    .mt-3{margin-top:18px;}
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <%- include('./partials/navbar.ejs') %>

  <!-- HERO -->
  <section class="about-hero">
    <div class="inner">
      <h1>About BookLantern</h1>
      <p>BookLantern brings together results from globally trusted libraries across the web so you can discover millions of books in one place.</p>
      <div class="cta-row">
        <a class="btn" href="/read">Browse Books</a>
        <a class="btn alt" href="/watch">Explore Videos</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- VALUE STRIP -->
  <section class="value-strip">
    <div class="container value-inner">
      <div class="value-item">
        <div class="vi-title">Millions+ titles</div>
        <div class="vi-copy">Search an ever-growing catalog brought together for easy discovery.</div>
      </div>
      <div class="value-item">
        <div class="vi-title">From globally trusted libraries</div>
        <div class="vi-copy">One search that unifies open stacks across the web.</div>
      </div>
      <div class="value-item">
        <div class="vi-title">One clean reader</div>
        <div class="vi-copy">Distraction-free pagination, bookmarks, and a consistent reading flow.</div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- MISSION -->
  <main class="section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="shelf-header">
        <h2>Our mission</h2>
        <div class="hint">Make finding and reading great books effortless</div>
      </div>
      <p class="section-copy">
        BookLantern helps the open book web feel like one great library. We organize results from
        reputable catalogs, then present them in a simple interface so readers can search once, save
        favorites, and pick up where they left off—without juggling different sites and accounts.
      </p>

      <div class="shelf-header mt-3">
        <h2>What makes BookLantern different</h2>
        <div class="hint">Clarity, speed, and focus</div>
      </div>
      <p class="section-copy">
        We prioritize reading experience. Pages turn quickly, controls stay out of the way, and your
        place is remembered across devices. When a title is available to read, we surface it clearly.
        When it isn’t, we point you to where it lives—no runaround, no clutter.
      </p>

      <div class="shelf-header mt-3">
        <h2>Our promise to readers</h2>
        <div class="hint">Access + delight</div>
      </div>
      <p class="section-copy">
        BookLantern exists to make books easier to reach and more enjoyable to read. We keep the
        experience calm and consistent, respect availability, and continuously expand the catalog so
        you can discover more with less effort.
      </p>
    </div>
  </main>

  <%- include('./partials/footer.ejs') %>

  <!-- About Page Scripts -->
  <script defer src="/js/about.js<%= buildId ? `?v=${buildId}` : '' %>"></script>
</body>
</html>
